1- Open XOX.exe.
2- Click on "Create a Room"/"Join a Room".
3.1- If you are creating the room you need to enter a name and then click "Create".
3.1.1- After creating the room you need to share the "Key" with the person you want to play with and wait untill they join. You can see it in the info bar if they join.
3.1.2- When they join you might need to make the first move.
3.2- If you have the room key you can join by entering your name and the key then clicking the "Join" button.
3.2.1- After joining, you might need to wait if it is the opponent's turn.
4-You can return to the lobby at anytime by clicking the return button or the quit button.
